					<msContents>
						<summary>

						<p>Records the erection of a platform (<hi rend="italic">sumai tāṅgi</hi>), in memory of one Lachchumāyi, who was the daughter of Kavalamuttu son of Kēthāralinga mudali, by her mother Paḻaniammā. Lachchumāyi's husband's name was Aruṇāchala mudali who was the son of Koḻundavēl mudali, a native of Kavuṇḍaṉpāḷaiyam village.</p>						

						</summary>
